  <h2><strong>User Testing</strong></h2>
  I sat down with OpenTable users to test out the usability of my designs. I asked them to interact with the walk in flow prototype as I gave general instructions. I took notes of mistaken clicks, expected (and missed) interactions, reactions, and questions:

  <img src="<%= image_path("images/project-opentable/user_testing.png") %>" class="zoomImages" alt="I took note of the users' comments and frustrations and organized them as cards under their respective screen."><br><br>

  <h2><strong>Next Iterations</strong></h2>
  I identified the problems and thought through ways I could eliminate the confusion and distress from the experience.

  <img src="<%= image_path("images/project-opentable/redesign_1.png") %>" class="zoomImages" alt="Redundant calls to action">
